[b]TLC
Profile:[/b]
American female R & B trio discovered by Pebbles. In the beginning the band was called "2nd Nature". 
"TLC" was based upon the first names of the original members: Tionne, Lisa and Crystal (founder of the band). Later, when Crystal Jones was replaced by Rozonda Thomas, the girls were given nicknames to be able to continue to use the acronym. (Tionne 'T-Boz' Watkins, Lisa 'Left-Eye' Lopes and Rozonda 'Chilli' Thomas) 
Lisa Lopes died in a car crash on April 25, 2002.
